{
 "fragments": [
  {
   "begin": "0.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "9.360", 
   "id": "s000001", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Pr\u00e4sident! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "9.360", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "10.080", 
   "id": "s000002", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kolleginnen und Kollegen! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "10.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "12.160", 
   "id": "s000003", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Liebe B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrger! "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "12.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "15.400", 
   "id": "s000004", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Dieser Bundesregierung fehlt die Orientierung darauf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "15.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "18.640", 
   "id": "s000005", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass wir in der Mobilit\u00e4t vor gro\u00dfen Ver\u00e4nderungen stehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "18.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "19.880", 
   "id": "s000006", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Minister Scheuer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "19.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "27.400", 
   "id": "s000007", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deutschland ist auch verkehrspolitisch kein Heimatmuseum und will auch keins werden."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "27.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "30.000", 
   "id": "s000008", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Es stehen extrem wichtige Themen auf der Tagesordnung. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "30.000", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "33.040", 
   "id": "s000009", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir m\u00fcssen den Aussto\u00df von Klimagasen senken, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "33.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "35.440", 
   "id": "s000010", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Infrastruktur selektiv erhalten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "35.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "36.880", 
   "id": "s000011", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "aber auch umbauen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "36.880", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "41.680", 
   "id": "s000012", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mobilit\u00e4t f\u00fcr alle bereitstellen und damit Arbeitspl\u00e4tze sichern. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "41.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "42.920", 
   "id": "s000013", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Als ich Ihnen zugeh\u00f6rt habe, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "42.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "44.160", 
   "id": "s000014", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Minister Scheuer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "44.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "46.160", 
   "id": "s000015", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "konnte ich leider nicht heraush\u00f6ren, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "46.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "49.400", 
   "id": "s000016", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie sich der Komplexit\u00e4t dieser Aufgaben bewusst sind."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "49.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "53.320", 
   "id": "s000017", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Statt den Interessen der Automobillobby zu folgen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "53.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "58.960", 
   "id": "s000018", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "muss die Bundesregierung den umfassenden Umbauprozess des Verkehrs steuern und moderieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "58.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "60.520", 
   "id": "s000019", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das w\u00e4re Ihre Aufgabe."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "60.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "64.640", 
   "id": "s000020", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auf einige Bereiche m\u00f6chte ich kurz eingehen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "64.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "66.480", 
   "id": "s000021", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Der Verkehr ist der einzige Sektor, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "66.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "69.280", 
   "id": "s000022", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dessen Beitrag zur Klimaerhitzung weiter steigt; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "69.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "71.200", 
   "id": "s000023", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wir haben das eben schon einmal geh\u00f6rt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "71.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "74.560", 
   "id": "s000024", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie l\u00e4hmen die Entwicklung eines umweltfreundlichen Verkehrs, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "74.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "80.440", 
   "id": "s000025", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "weil Sie keine klaren Anforderungen wie deutliche CO 2 -Vorgaben oder Tempolimits stellen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "80.440", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "82.680", 
   "id": "s000026", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Ich sage Ihnen klar und deutlich: "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "82.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "89.600", 
   "id": "s000027", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die sch\u00fctzende Hand der Bundesregierung \u00fcber die Chefetagen der Automobilindustrie heute schafft die Krisen von morgen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "89.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "103.760", 
   "id": "s000028", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Auch beim Thema Infrastruktur setzen Sie vollkommen einseitig auf den Ausbau der Stra\u00dfen und wollen mit einer Erh\u00f6hung um 11\u00a0Prozent auf insgesamt 6,8\u00a0Milliarden Euro weitere Rekordsummen investieren. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "103.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "106.920", 
   "id": "s000029", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir brauchen aber nicht mehr Stra\u00dfen und Autobahnen. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "106.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "113.160", 
   "id": "s000030", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Stattdessen sollten Sie endlich das von Ihnen selbst proklamierte Ziel \u201eErhalt geht vor Neubau\u201c wirklich umsetzen."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "113.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "117.760", 
   "id": "s000031", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Beim Thema Bahn kommen Sie ebenfalls nicht von der Stelle. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "117.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "120.200", 
   "id": "s000032", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Statt die Mittel f\u00fcr den Ausbau zu erh\u00f6hen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "120.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "123.080", 
   "id": "s000033", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie gerade noch im Koalitionsvertrag versprochen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "123.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.560", 
   "id": "s000034", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "k\u00fcrzen Sie sie allein in diesem Haushaltsjahr um ganze 5,5\u00a0Prozent\u00a0\u2013 "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.560", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "127.680", 
   "id": "s000035", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "es ist nicht so, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "127.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "129.280", 
   "id": "s000036", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wie Sie eben behauptet haben, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "129.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "130.480", 
   "id": "s000037", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass sie gleich blieben\u00a0\u2013, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "130.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "136.080", 
   "id": "s000038", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "nachdem bereits im letzten Jahr 12\u00a0Prozent dieser Mittel gar nicht erst ausgegeben wurden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "136.080", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "139.680", 
   "id": "s000039", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "So jedenfalls wird es auch in Zukunft keine Fortschritte bei der Bahn geben. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "139.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "142.040", 
   "id": "s000040", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das ist verkehrspolitischer Unsinn."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "142.040", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "146.280", 
   "id": "s000041", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Kommen wir zu unserem Dauerthema, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "146.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "148.160", 
   "id": "s000042", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "der ungel\u00f6sten Dieselkrise. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "148.160", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "150.600", 
   "id": "s000043", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Sie hatten mehr als zweieinhalb Jahre Zeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "150.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "151.720", 
   "id": "s000044", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "L\u00f6sungen zu finden. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "151.720", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "152.760", 
   "id": "s000045", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Das Ergebnis? "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "152.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "154.680", 
   "id": "s000046", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die Autos vergiften weiter die Luft, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "154.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "158.400", 
   "id": "s000047", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die T\u00e4ter laufen frei herum und betr\u00fcgen ungestraft weiter. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "158.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "162.760", 
   "id": "s000048", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Die betrogenen Autobesitzer bleiben auf ihrem Schaden sitzen und Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "162.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "163.960", 
   "id": "s000049", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Herr Minister Scheuer, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "163.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "165.760", 
   "id": "s000050", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "t\u00e4uschen die \u00d6ffentlichkeit, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "165.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "175.200", 
   "id": "s000051", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "indem Sie Softwareupdates als die beste L\u00f6sung pr\u00e4sentieren und gleichzeitig Ihr eigenes Regierungsgutachten seit mehr als vier Monaten zur\u00fcckhalten, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "175.200", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "178.240", 
   "id": "s000052", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "das genau zu diesen Hardwarenachr\u00fcstungen r\u00e4t."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "178.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "182.680", 
   "id": "s000053", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wir Linke erinnern Sie mit den Worten der Deutschen Umwelthilfe gern daran, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "182.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "192.480", 
   "id": "s000054", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "dass Sie einen Eid auf das Wohl der B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrger geschworen haben und nicht etwa auf die Profitmaximierung der Automobilkonzerne."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "192.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "197.520", 
   "id": "s000055", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Zum Thema Steuerverschwendung durch \u00d6PP haben wir ja heute schon einiges geh\u00f6rt. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "197.520", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "198.680", 
   "id": "s000056", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Anders als Sie, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "198.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "199.640", 
   "id": "s000057", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die Bundesregierung, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "199.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "208.760", 
   "id": "s000058", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "haben wir als Linke mit unserem Konzept eines sozialen und \u00f6kologischen Umbaus eine klare Orientierung hin zur Zukunft der mobilen Gesellschaft. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "208.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "212.480", 
   "id": "s000059", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mobilit\u00e4t ist wichtige Grundlage gesellschaftlicher Teilhabe. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "212.480", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "215.600", 
   "id": "s000060", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Wie eben schon mein Kollege Victor Perli ausgef\u00fchrt hat, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "215.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "221.400", 
   "id": "s000061", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "wollen rund 80 bis 90\u00a0Prozent der Menschen im Land lieber weniger auf das Auto angewiesen sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "221.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "228.320", 
   "id": "s000062", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Deshalb muss das Herzst\u00fcck einer Mobilit\u00e4t f\u00fcr alle ein attraktiver Umweltverbund aller Verkehrstr\u00e4ger sein. "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "228.320", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "231.680", 
   "id": "s000063", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Mit diesem Umweltverbund aus Elektrofahrzeugen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "231.680", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "233.600", 
   "id": "s000064", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "mehr und bezahlbaren Bahnen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "233.600", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.120", 
   "id": "s000065", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "\u00d6PNV, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.120", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "234.800", 
   "id": "s000066", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Rad- "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "234.800", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "237.960", 
   "id": "s000067", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und Fu\u00dfverkehr k\u00f6nnen die B\u00fcrgerinnen und B\u00fcrger, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "237.960", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "243.280", 
   "id": "s000068", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "unterst\u00fctzt durch die M\u00f6glichkeiten der Digitalisierung und den Trend des Teilens, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "243.280", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "246.840", 
   "id": "s000069", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "die f\u00fcr sie jeweils passende Fortbewegungsart selbst w\u00e4hlen; "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "246.840", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "250.400", 
   "id": "s000070", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "sie schonen damit Umwelt und Gesundheit und mindern den Ressourcenverbrauch."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "250.400", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "252.920", 
   "id": "s000071", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "H\u00f6ren Sie endlich auf, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "252.920", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "255.240", 
   "id": "s000072", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "allein auf den Stra\u00dfenverkehr zu setzen, "
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "255.240", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "257.760", 
   "id": "s000073", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "und schaffen Sie endlich die l\u00e4ngst \u00fcberf\u00e4llige echte Verkehrswende!"
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "257.760", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "258.640", 
   "id": "s000074", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "Vielen Dank."
   ]
  }, 
  {
   "begin": "258.640", 
   "children": [], 
   "end": "269.000", 
   "id": "s000075", 
   "language": "deu", 
   "lines": [
    "N\u00e4chster Redner f\u00fcr B\u00fcndnis\u00a090/Die Gr\u00fcnen ist der Kollege Cem \u00d6zdemir."
   ]
  }
 ]
}